{
  "stem": "15393.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had no way of getting out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was totally, totally unhappy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my mother was coming on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Again, the worry, did she manage to get through the town, taking off the armband, taking this off, detaching.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was stitched on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So she had to put something on top of herself.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It wasn't to take it off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She had to put another-- a shawl or something over it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to walk through the town, A, nobody would recognize her, somebody who might have known her before, should not recognize her now.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "B, to be able to get out of the ghetto, with some group, detach you-- herself and not be spotted by anyone, that she does that, and walk all through the town, walking, walking, walking to come here, in order to sit all through Sunday and so forth, huh?",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Sunday, at 4 o'clock in the morning, leave in the dark to go through the whole town, where there is a curfew.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One is not allowed to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She did it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- I mean, how can I relate this, to give a-- a-- a picture of what it really was like?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was an unbelievable situation, even though I was in-- in-- in a very safe, or so it would have appeared, haven for those days.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So at one point, I said to Frau Wieth, I'm not staying.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I really-- I appreciate, but I'm-- I want-- I'm going back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was throwing-- sorry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were groups, Jewish groups walking to work, going to work and passing our windows.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were on the third floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Occasionally, I'd roll something, you know, throw down to a group and something.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it would be, please, see if my mother is alive.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
